CONSTANTS Goal = 4   \* We want to make sure that we can get at least    *)
                      * this much oil from a single refill of our jug, so*)
                      * the goal is to have enough fuel for exactly n     *)
                      * trips. The value of Goal must be greater than or  *)
                      * equal to 4 and less than or equal to 1023         *)
